javascript:
    it is a scripting langauage 
    it is used to create dynamic and interactive webpages
    it is a client side language 
    it is used to add behavior and functionalities to webpages 
    it is synchronous langauge /it is executed line by line
    it is case sensitive

javaxcripts also used in:
    1.Angular
    2.React
    3.Vuejs
    4.NodeJs 

js current version : ECMAScript 13 (ES13)
ECMA- europeon computer manufaturer association

if we want to create js file 
    ______.js extension

-----------------------------------
we can include js in 3 ways:
inline js
internal js
external js


-----------------------------------
inline js:

<button script=""></button>

internal js:

<script></script>

external js:

<script src="filename.js"></script>
-----------------------------------
